dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents telephone exchange boundaries for Wisconsin as of November 1, 2000. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Department of Administration in 2000.[his data layer is a polygon shapefile of the telephone exchange boundaries in Wisconsin, derived from the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources' 1:24,000 landnet coverage. This data set is referenced to the Wisconsin Transverse Mercator (WTM) projection system, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
